      "blocks": {
        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Gold has been treasured for centuries in India, not only as a symbol of wealth but also as a representation of trust, tradition, and family heritage. When it comes to purchasing gold jewellery, authenticity is crucial, and this is where the 22k gold hallmark becomes an essential indicator. Within the first moments of buying, the hallmark assures you that the jewellery contains 91.6% pure gold and has been certified by recognized authorities.</p><p>In this article, we will cover everything about 22 carat gold hallmark—its meaning, components, how to check it, tips for buying, and why hallmarked gold is considered a valuable investment. Whether you are shopping for a wedding, festival, or a personal collection, understanding the 22 carat gold hallmark will help you make informed and secure decisions.</p><p>By the end, you will be able to confidently identify genuine hallmarked gold and understand the importance of choosing 22 carat gold hallmark jewellery over uncertified options.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What is a 22 Carat Gold Hallmark?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>What is a 22 Carat Gold Hallmark?</h2>",
            "custom_id": "22carat",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_gEUkmH": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/What_is_a_22_Carat_Gold_Hallmark.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A 22 carat gold hallmark is more than just an engraving; it is a seal of purity, authenticity, and quality. Gold is measured in carats, and 22K gold contains 91.6% pure gold, with the remaining 8.4% made up of alloys to improve durability. This makes 22K gold strong enough for intricate designs while maintaining its rich, classic yellow hue.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-22ct-half-eternity-bezel-diamond-band",
              "classic-diamond-solitaire-mens-engagement-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JmwFBb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The hallmark guarantees that your jewellery has been tested and certified by the Bureau of Indian Standards (BIS), India’s official authority for gold purity. It assures you that the jewellery you are purchasing is genuine, protects you from fraud, and maintains the integrity of your investment. Without the 22 carat gold hallmark, there is no way to confirm whether the gold meets the official purity standards.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jc4E4r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Hallmarking Matters for 22 Carat Gold Jewellery",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Hallmarking Matters for 22 Carat Gold Jewellery</h2><p>Hallmarking is not just a formality; it is a necessary safeguard for anyone buying gold. The importance of the 22 carat gold hallmark includes:</p>",
            "custom_id": "importance",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6WCWXy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Components of a 22 Carat Gold Hallmark",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Components of a 22 Carat Gold Hallmark</h3>",
            "custom_id": "components",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_AWtNat": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Components_of_a_22_Carat_Gold_Hallmark.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Every 22 carat gold hallmark consists of multiple elements that ensure its authenticity and traceability. The key components include:</p><ul><li>BIS Logo: The official certification mark confirming the gold has been tested and approved.</li><li>Purity Mark (916): Indicates that the gold is 91.6% pure, which is the standard for 22K jewellery.</li><li>Assaying & Hallmarking Centre’s Mark: Shows which certified lab tested the jewellery.</li><li>Jeweller’s Identification Mark: Identifies the manufacturer or retailer responsible for the piece.</li><li>HUID Number (6-digit unique code): A unique code assigned to each piece of hallmarked jewellery from 2023 onward for traceability.</li></ul><p>Understanding these components is essential to verify the authenticity of any 22 carat gold hallmark jewellery you buy.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "golden-solitaire-diamond-mens-ring",
              "double-halo-round-diamond-bracelet"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xii4nX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Check a 22 Carat Gold Hallmark",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>How to Check a 22 Carat Gold Hallmark</h3>",
            "custom_id": "check",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_XJgEXF": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/How_to_Check_a_22_Carat_Gold_Hallmark_3e978921-1d2a-477d-b793-79806196b217.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Ensuring that your 22K gold jewellery is genuine requires careful inspection. Follow these steps to check a 22 carat gold hallmark:</p><ol><li>Locate the hallmark symbols: Check inside bangles, rings, pendants, or chains where the hallmark is usually engraved.</li><li>Verify the HUID number with the BIS Care App: Scan the unique 6-digit number to confirm certification and traceability.</li><li>Cross-check invoice and certification details: Ensure that the listed purity, weight, and price match the hallmark.</li></ol>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "mens-two-tone-hexagonal-cluster-diamond-ring",
              "mens-textured-solitaire-lgd-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_zLUXk4": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>4. Inspect the jewellery for authenticity signs: Look for clear, consistent markings; avoid jewellery with smudged or incomplete stamps.</p><p>5. Consult a trusted jeweller if in doubt: A certified jeweller can perform quick tests to verify purity.</p><p>By following these steps, you can confidently purchase 22 carat gold hallmark jewellery without worrying about authenticity.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_rQKzCe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Comparing Gold Purities: Why Choose 22K Hallmarked Jewellery",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Comparing Gold Purities: Why Choose 22K Hallmarked Jewellery</h2><p>Gold comes in different purities, and understanding the differences helps in choosing the right jewellery. Here’s a comparison in detail:</p><ul><li>24K Gold: 99.9% pure; very soft; best for investments but not ideal for everyday wear.</li><li>22K Gold: 91.6% pure; combines high purity with durability; ideal for wedding jewellery, bangles, and necklaces.</li><li>18K Gold: 75% pure; stronger than 22K; used for daily wear and designer pieces.</li><li>14K Gold: 58.5% pure; highly durable; commonly used for fashion jewellery and affordable options.</li></ul><p>The 22 carat gold hallmark ensures you get the perfect balance between purity and wearability, making it a preferred choice for traditional and modern jewellery buyers alike.</p>",
            "custom_id": "comparison",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ADDTPa": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Buying Guide: Smart Tips for Hallmarked Jewellery",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Buying Guide: Smart Tips for Hallmarked Jewellery</h2><p>Purchasing hallmarked jewellery requires careful attention. Here are some smart tips when buying 22 carat gold hallmark pieces:</p><ul><li>Always ask for BIS certification before purchase.</li><li>Check making charges and weight to avoid overpaying.</li><li>Compare prices across multiple jewellers for transparency.</li><li>Understand color variations: yellow, rose, or white gold.</li><li>Prefer trusted jewellers and certified online platforms.</li><li>Inspect jewellery carefully for a clear and legible 22 carat gold hallmark.</li><li>Avoid purchasing jewellery from uncertified sources or street vendors.</li></ul><p>These tips will ensure that your 22 carat gold hallmark jewellery purchase is safe, authentic, and worthwhile.</p>",
            "custom_id": "buying",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7bxGmb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "22 Carat Gold Hallmark as an Investment",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>22 Carat Gold Hallmark as an Investment</h2>",
            "custom_id": "investment",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_gB8tne": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/22_Carat_Gold_Hallmark_as_an_Investment_1080_1080.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Hallmarked 22K gold is not just for personal use—it is also a long-term investment. The advantages include:</p><ul><li>High Liquidity and Resale Value: Hallmarked gold can be easily sold or exchanged due to certified purity.</li><li>Legacy and Heirloom Value: Hallmarked jewellery can be passed down through generations while retaining trust and worth.</li><li>Financial Security: Buying hallmarked 22K gold is a reliable way to safeguard your savings against market fluctuations.</li><li>Emotional Value: Hallmarked jewellery preserves its significance, making it perfect for gifts, weddings, and family traditions.</li></ul><p>A 22 carat gold hallmark ensures both financial and sentimental value, combining wealth protection with emotional satisfaction.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CNg3En": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion</h2><p>A 22 carat gold hallmark is your assurance of authenticity, purity, and investment security. From traditional bangles to contemporary necklaces, hallmarked jewellery ensures your purchase is trustworthy and valuable. Always verify the hallmark, check the HUID number, and buy from certified jewellers to make informed choices.</p><p>At Lucira Jewelry, we believe luxury should be ethical, pure, and timeless. While hallmarked 22K gold secures trust, our lab-grown diamond jewellery offers a sustainable way to celebrate beauty responsibly. Explore our<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"> collection</a> and discover jewellery designed to shine ethically, just like you.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
